    r'$\bullet\ k_{\mathrm{ESIPT}} \sim 10^{13}\ \mathrm{s}^{-1}$: Sub-100 fs proton transfer.' '\n'
    r'$\bullet\ k_{\mathrm{cleavage}} \sim 10^{11}\ \mathrm{s}^{-1}$: Picosecond bond rupture.' '\n'
    r'$\bullet$ Hierarchical timescales ensure efficient energy funneling.'
)
